{"tid":2384064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應BNO簽證　外交部：對香港的光明未來充滿信心","createTime":"2021-01-28T10:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T11:25:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"556c43f3a159823603ecad6dcdf3f6926fd5ac27","tid":2384064,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572862-20210128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572862-20210128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=d3551103\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572862-20210128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2f0ebd51\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572862-20210128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府本月31日起，接受合資格申請英國國民海外護照BNO的港人，申請簽證到當地工作或留學。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅表示，中方已多次表明嚴正立場，指出英方違背承諾，一意孤行，反覆炒作英國國民海外護照問題，干預香港事務，干預中國內政，到頭來只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅重申，對香港的光明未來充滿信心，任何勢力、任何情況都動搖不到中國政府和人民維護國家主權、安全，維護香港繁榮穩定，反對外部干預的決心和意志。"},{"pid":"72bbd9ce7068de7847c9c4ba766772e236af31bf","tid":2384064,"uid":389613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n淨係走錢無用，人都最好走埋！！你每年最少響香港幫佢賺緊 18 萬，當一蚊都唔加你，做 45 年野係 810 萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未計你養仔又要洗 400 萬，又未計呢個只係你份糧，仲未計香港班人渣老細用你既血同汗賺既大量財富 *班 pk 可能比1蚊你但賺緊4-5蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">絕對唔好睇少自己，你淨係個人走都搞死港共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更重要係，你走香港班仆街藍絲要頂埋你交果做稅 (that's why 屯地波要加稅)，到時班賣港賊佢地就真係活響人間地獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"dc517cfbd4d8a74a2fad45743f6940242d77f787","tid":2384064,"uid":323157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"d91f6b9871037729e5766d079944244a8f6148c2","tid":2384064,"uid":279938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"即係冇反制啦"},{"pid":"c5ebd1ad0ebb19f96c5f2605534ff58398d2a5cf","tid":2384064,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"屌廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be107f4a13aab62180e040e1d896fc2ded16a39d","tid":2384064,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91f6b9871037729e5766d079944244a8f6148c2","tid":2384064,"uid":279938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"即係冇反制啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"反轉電掣？"},{"pid":"df73c346a1545e87700b6133c847cdb2e8cfdca9","tid":2384064,"uid":162882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"即係點? 係咪封機場唔俾出境?"},{"pid":"66da17e3a0962874a9279c7102f15d3651dc83df","tid":2384064,"uid":33622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大聲無貨賣"},{"pid":"e1a9acbca19ea8c477ce0e0ce1d9858271e5f2ef","tid":2384064,"uid":238117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"縮陽入腹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f815282a48c6d635e5d025498d1dbac9aba96d97","tid":2384064,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"你咪由人去做二等公民囉, 關你撚事咩<br />\n譚惠珠話唔滿意就走架嘛, 入佢數岩架喇"},{"pid":"4d9415917bb7a7efcc08450ca646d02970510c87","tid":2384064,"uid":50526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"走到嘅好走<img src=\"